I agree, but I was asking Bruce, trying to compare the difference in 
the sounds (12-469 vs 12-470) as the radios scan.  The RS 12-469 has 
a &quot;click&quot; while sweeping the bands, especially through AM; I am not 
hearing it with the RS 12-470 recordings by Bruce and others.  Thus, 
I wanted to see what the set-up Bruce was using to see if it would 
make a difference in reducing my audio capture of the &quot;click.&quot;

LC

